summary: Completed comprehensive testing of expense tracker app - all backend APIs and frontend functionality working perfectly
passed_tests: Backend API - All 22 endpoints working (auth, income, expenses, budget, credit cards, recurring, analytics)
Frontend Registration - User can successfully create account
Frontend Navigation - All pages accessible (Dashboard, Income, Expenses, Budget, Credit Cards, Recurring, Analytics)
Income Management - Add, view, delete income entries with recurring options
Expense Management - Add, view, delete expenses with categories and payment methods
Budget Management - Set monthly budgets with category breakdowns and alerts
Credit Card Management - Add, view, delete credit cards
Recurring Items - Process recurring income/expense items
Analytics - Charts and trends displaying properly
CAD Currency Formatting - All amounts displayed in Canadian dollars
UI/UX - Modern dark theme with purple/pink gradients working well
Data Persistence - All data saving and loading correctly
JWT Authentication - Token-based auth working properly
